Secure Docker Images with Grype & Docker Bench
Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Install and configure Grype vulnerability scanner and Docker Bench Security
Scan Docker images for known vulnerabilities and security misconfigurations
Interpret vulnerability scan results and prioritize remediation efforts
Automate security scanning with Python scripts
Implement Docker security best practices and hardening techniques
