Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Grype database update fails

Check internet connectivity
Verify disk space availability
Try manual update: grype db update --verbose
Issue: Docker Bench requires sudo

Docker Bench needs root access for system checks
Run with: sudo ./docker-bench-security.sh
Review permissions on Docker socket
Issue: Python scripts fail with import errors

Install required packages: pip3 install --user <package>
Verify Python 3 is default: python3 --version
Check script has execute permissions
Issue: High vulnerability counts on older images

This is expected for outdated base images
Update to latest stable versions
Consider switching to Alpine-based images
Issue: Docker daemon configuration not applied

Verify JSON syntax in /etc/docker/daemon.json
Restart Docker: sudo systemctl restart docker
Check logs: sudo journalctl -u docker
